I really wanted to say a big thank you to Austen- Ham-Howes for all his help in our clinic. 
Our journey as a clinic has been a exciting, challenging and sometimes down right exhausting but we have grown from small 1 room clinic to an established and busy 4 room clinic in the hart of Richmond!

He has had the vision, given us targets and has provided us with strategy to help us attain these goals. 
He is a chartered accountant and helps us with our tax and accounts too making sure our money goes as far as possible.

I would highly recommend him to anyone who wants to grow there business. He has worked wonders for us!

Follow our list of alphabetical careers. B - Bookkeepers perform general accounting duties. They maintain financial records, keep track of accounts and are employed by private businesses and virtually every institution.  Bookkeepers should have good numeracy skills, attention to detail, ability to work to deadlines, good communication skills and experience in using software such as Excel. A full charge bookkeeper will need a bachelor's degree in finance, accounting or business, although you can start with an internship. #bookkeeper #bookkeeping #business #internships #accounts #accounting #finance #money #jobs #careers #bookkeepers
